The paper deals with extending propositional logic to a logic of plausible reasoning, which is a topic closely related to artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses probability theory, which is a topic in cryptography and security (cs.CR) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper deals with propositional logic, which falls under the sub-category of programming languages (cs.PL).
